---
---
<section class="py-24 sm:py-36 px-6 sm:px-10 lg:px-14 bg-[var(--color-soft)] relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background washes -->
  <div class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-[var(--color-sunshine)]/25 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 -right-32 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full bg-[var(--color-pink)]/50 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 sm:gap-10 items-center relative z-10">
    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 reveal order-1 text-center lg:text-right">
      <span class="ltr inline-block bg-[var(--color-ocean)] text-[var(--color-soft)] text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
        ★ A Personal Invite
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-[var(--color-ink)] leading-[1.05]">
        המילה<br/>של <span class="text-[var(--color-coral)]">יעל</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-[var(--color-muted)] text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0">
        איך זה באמת מרגיש להיות חלק מהקהילה?
        יעל מספרת מניסיון אישי על האווירה, החבר'ה, ולמה ממש כדאי לכם לקפוץ לאירוע הבא שלנו.
        <span class="block mt-2 opacity-70">(שימו אוזניות).</span>
      </p>
      <div class="mt-7 flex items-center gap-3 justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <span class="text-3xl text-[var(--color-coral)] animate-bounce">↓</span>
        <span class="ltr text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)]">Press Play</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Video -->
    <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 reveal-scale order-2">
      <div class="relative rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0_40px_80px_-20px_rgba(31,20,16,0.4)] bg-[var(--color-ink)]">
        <video
          src="/images/video.mp4"
          controls
          playsinline
          preload="metadata"
          poster="/images/IMG_4498.jpg"
          class="w-full h-auto block"
        >
          הדפדפן שלך לא תומך בנגן וידאו.
        </video>
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 ltr text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase font-bold text-[var(--color-ink)] bg-[var(--color-sunshine)] px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full">
          ★ Yael · TLV Young
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
